name: Fighters Straight Ahead
Lore: 'Sometimes a swarm of starfighters can look more imposing than it really is. Mostly though, it''s just best to avoid them altogether.',
Text: 'Deploy on table. Your Force generation is +1 at systems you control. Opponent''s non-unique starfighters are deploy +1 (or +2 to a system you occupy). (Immune to Alter.)',
